ults for both reddening and distance. Application of this method to an\nOGLE-II field, and the results by Alves et al.(2002), confirm a LMC distance\nmodulus of about 18.50, in agreement with the HST extragalactic distance scale\nzero-point. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Aug 2002 14:54:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
