0-dimensional super Yang Mills\ntheory and 11-dimensional M-theory are briefly discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2002 20:41:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Aug 2002 04:41:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Oct 2002 18:51:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
